Add runtime detection for:
- GPIO_BASE: 512 on Noble/6.8, 0 on Jammy/5.15
- NVMEM_PATH: 3-00501 on Noble, 3-00500 on Jammy

Use computed paths in servo reset and EEPROM tests.
